      "content": "it's not even terrifying to me though. that's the weird part. it actually sounds kind of peaceful. like, if i'm already a ghost, then just finally disappearing... it wouldn't be a big deal. it would just be quiet. don't you think? if someone is already invisible, there's no real harm in just being gone, right?",
